metadata.name: Chalet #1 - Alps
metadata.description: Inspired by the Swiss Alps, the Exclusible Chalet has the right balance of charm and modernity. Surrounded by snow magic and stunning mountain views, this is Exclusible's latest metaverse real estate project. Designed especially as a gift for our community to the smallest detail, the Exclusible Chalet has the virtual magic and unique feel that only snow and mountains provide.
